  - Keeper
  dialogue:
  - Pick up the rod and look for what you want to catch.
  - Once you've caught one it'll go in that barrel there. You can check how much
    you've caught by interacting with the scale [E].
  - Also be sure to be wary of your time out here. You'll only want to spend so much
    time amongst the waves.
